{
    "id": "tween",
    "name": "Tween Animation",
    "isScript": false,
    "description": "A powerful tween animation system for smoothly interpolating object transforms (position, rotation, scale) over time. Supports 20+ easing functions, three loop modes, and trigger-based or automatic playback. Uses @tweenjs/tween.js for high-quality animation curves. Perfect for creating polished motion without keyframe animation.",
    "documentation": "## Tween Animation\nAnimate object position, rotation, and scale using easing functions.\n\n### Transform\n- **Move** - Translation offset (X, Y, Z)\n- **Rotate** - Rotation in degrees (X, Y, Z)\n- **Scale** - Scale change (X, Y, Z)\n\n### Timing\n- **Speed** - Animation speed (0-100)\n- **Ease Type** - Easing curve (Linear, Quad, Cubic, Bounce, Elastic, etc.)\n- **Loop Mode** - None (play once), Repeat, or Mirror (ping-pong)\n\n### Tips\n- Use **Start on Trigger** with a Trigger behavior for interactive animations\n- Mirror loop mode creates smooth back-and-forth motion\n- Combine with Platform for custom moving objects\n- Supports 28 different easing functions for varied motion styles",
    "author": "stemstudio",
    "tags": ["motion"],
    "main": "TweenAnimationBehavior.ts",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "dependencies": {},
    "throttleConfig": {
        "throttlePriority": "MEDIUM",
        "enableFrustumCulling": true,
        "enableDistanceThrottling": true,
        "requiresConsistentUpdates": false
    },
    "attributes": {
        "customName": {
            "name": "Custom Name",
            "type": "string"
        },
        "startOnTrigger": {
            "name": "Start on trigger",
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": false,
            "description": "When enabled, the tween only plays when activated by a Trigger behavior instead of starting automatically."
        },
        "move": {
            "name": "Move",
            "type": "vector3",
            "default": {
                "x": 0,
                "y": 0,
                "z": 0
            },
            "description": "Translation offset applied to the object over the tween duration along each axis (X, Y, Z)."
        },
        "rotate": {
            "name": "Rotate",
            "type": "vector3",
            "default": {
                "x": 0,
                "y": 0,
                "z": 0
            },
            "description": "Rotation offset in degrees applied to the object over the tween duration along each axis (X, Y, Z)."
        },
        "scale": {
            "name": "Scale",
            "type": "vector3",
            "default": {
                "x": 0,
                "y": 0,
                "z": 0
            },
            "description": "Scale change applied to the object over the tween duration along each axis (X, Y, Z)."
        },
        "speed": {
            "name": "Speed",
            "type": "number",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "default": 1,
            "description": "Controls how fast the tween animation plays. Higher values result in faster animation."
        },
        "easing": {
            "name": "Ease Type",
            "type": "enum",
            "options": [
                {
                    "label": "Linear",
                    "value": "linear"
                },
                {
                    "label": "Quad In",
